any as 11,000 visitors who wish to relax in its quiet charm and beauty.</p>\r\n                                    <br />\r\n                                    <div class=\"gallery1\">\r\n								        <div class=\"gallery1_inner clear\">								\r\n                                            <center>\r\n								                <a href=\"./images/tmp/template_blue-sky_large.jpg\" rel=\"gallery-2\" title=\"Image caption.\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"./images/tmp/template_blue-sky_thumb.jpg\" /></a>\r\n								                <a href=\"./images/tmp/template_gold-sky_large.jpg\" rel=\"gallery-2\" title=\"Image caption.\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"./images/tmp/template_gold-sky_thumb.jpg\" /></a>\r\n								                <a href=\"./images/tmp/template_lightblue-sky_large.jpg\" rel=\"gallery-2\" title=\"Image caption.\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"./images/tmp/template_lightblue-sky_thumb.jpg\" /></a>								        \r\n                                                <a href=\"./images/tmp/template_blue-sky_large.jpg\" rel=\"gallery-2\" title=\"Image caption.\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"./images/tmp/template_blue-sky_thumb.jpg\" /></a>\r\n								                <a href=\"./images/tmp/template_gold-sky_large.jpg\" rel=\"gallery-2\" title=\"Image caption.\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"./images/tmp/template_gold-sky_thumb.jpg\" /></a>\r\n								                <a href=\"./images/tmp/template_lightblue-sky_large.jpg\" rel=\"gallery-2\" title=\"Image caption.\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"./images/tmp/template_lightblue-sky_thumb.jpg\" /></a>								        \r\n                                                <a href=\"./images/tmp/template_blue-sky_large.jpg\" rel=\"gallery-2\" title=\"Image caption.\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"./images/tmp/template_blue-sky_thumb.jpg\" /></a>\r\n								                <a href=\"./images/tmp/template_gold-sky_large.jpg\" rel=\"gallery-2\" title=\"Image caption.\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"./images/tmp/template_gold-sky_thumb.jpg\" /></a>\r\n								                <a href=\"./images/tmp/